  "title": "Videographer + Social Media",
  "description": "<p>Seeking an independent and detail-oriented social media + content intern/ junior executive to support social media content creation. The ideal candidate should be familiar with video creation and video edit. <br /></p><p>Photography & Videography</p><ul><li>Ability to shoot and edit content</li><li>Interior walkthrough videos, both short and long form</li><li>Short-form video clips for Instagram, TikTok, and XHS</li><li>Basic lifestyle and branding visuals for marketing use</li></ul><p>Design & Marketing Support</p><ul><li>Support in designing property flyers, EDMs, and brochures to enhance outreach</li><li>Adapt visuals for online and offline marketing formats</li></ul><p>Market & Content Support</p><ul><li>Collate pricing and project details to support marketing narratives</li><li>Assist with visual presentation of data where required</li></ul><p>Editing Scope</p><ul><li>Cinematic edit</li><li>Clean simple transitions</li><li>Light background music when appropriate</li></ul><p><br />Equipment</p><ul><li>Own camera and stabilisation equipment</li></ul><p><br />Ideal Candidate</p><ul><li>Reliable, organised, and detail-oriented</li><li>Open to feedback and collaboration</li><li>Strong familiarity with social media platforms, content creation, and digital marketing tools. Strong in spotting social media trends.</li><li>Portfolio with video editing examples</li><li>Excellent communication, research, and organisational skills. Ability to work on weekends and adapt to a flexible schedule.</li><li>Strong proficiency in video editing tools like CapCut or Adobe Premiere Pro.</li><li>Strong proficiency in Canva, Photoshop or similar design tools.</li></ul><p><br />Work Arrangement</p><ul><li>Min. 6 months internship or Retainer-based or Project-based (flexible to discuss)</li><li>Flexible working environment - at home or outbound</li></ul>",
